    question_name: "<p>If sin&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\theta\)</span> + cos&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\theta\)</span> =&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\sqrt2\)</span> cos <span class="math-tex">\(\theta\)</span>, (<span class="math-tex">\(\theta\)</span>&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\neq0^\circ)\)</span>&nbsp;then the value of&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(tan\,\theta\)</span>&nbsp;is:</p>",
