    <p><span class="math-tex">\(\Rightarrow\)</span>&nbsp;tan&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\theta\)</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\sqrt2\)</span>&nbsp;- 1.</p>",
