    <p><span class="math-tex">\(\Rightarrow\)</span>&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(1-cos^2A\)</span>&nbsp;= 1 - sin A&nbsp; <strong>............(ii)</strong></p>
    
    <p><strong>Now,</strong></p>
    
