    e_answer_describe: "<p><strong><img alt="" src="https://dk7h1f5gq849l.cloudfront.net/photos/questions/2022-01-11-131038-1-Windows-Photo-Viewer-1641887066-37ba0591-a425-4597-8a07-6e73531f4c3d.png" style="height:125px; width:147px" /></strong></p>
    
    <p>3 cos&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\theta\)</span>&nbsp;= 1,</p>
    
    <p>gives&nbsp;cos&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\theta\)</span>&nbsp;=&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\frac13\)</span></p>
    
    <p>Here B = 1, H = 3</p>
    
    <p><span class="math-tex">\(\therefore P=\sqrt{H^2-B^2}=\sqrt{9-1}=\sqrt{8}\)</span></p>
    
    <p><span class="math-tex">\(\therefore\)</span>&nbsp;cosec&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\theta\)</span>&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(=\frac3{\sqrt8}\)</span>&nbsp;<em>i.e.,</em>&nbsp;<span class="math-tex">\(\frac3{2\sqrt2}.\)</span></p>",
